content.description: Loads from Metal staging layer to the Bronze tables. SCD2(maintains history of the records, active records are open ended and old ones have closed date)
content.name: cdi_map_adm_subproducer_guidewire_bronze_load

object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	metal.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		metal.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code = 'ADM'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress' ) )
select
	distinct
	metal_asg.source_name,
	metal_asg.load_type,
	metal_asg.agency_nup,
	metal_asg.created,
	metal_asg.id,
	metal_asg.modified,
	metal_asg.status,
	metal_asg.sub_code,
	metal_asg.subproducer_cancelled_date,
	metal_asg.subproducer_name,
	metal_asg.subproducer_start_date,
	current_batch.batch_id
from
	metal.adm_subproducer_guidewire metal_asg
cross join current_batch
order by
	metal_asg.id,
	metal_asg.created,
	metal_asg.modified;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

object.customQuery:
select
	subproducer_guidewire_row_id,
	subproducer_guidewire_row_md5checksum,
	subproducer_guidewire_batch_id,
	agency_id,
	subproducer_guidewire_id,
	subproducer_guidewire_datetime_modified,
	subproducer_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime
from
	bronze.adm_subproducer_guidewire
where
	subproducer_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
